==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ἀήρ / aēr /  ah-ayr'
*From [[ἄημι]] aēmi (to breathe unconsciously, that is, respire; by analogy to blow); “air” (as naturally circumambient): 

===Noun===
